messages.subject: New Website
messages.msgSnippet: Our website is up and running!!! LeaAnn is checking it as I write, to make sure everything is working. Everyone that emailed me about the list of ideas from my
messages.messageBody:
Our website is up and running!!! LeaAnn is checking it as I write, to make
sure everything is working.
Everyone that emailed me about the list of ideas from my conference workshop
can go to our website and find the list (hopefully, if it's all working ok).
So if anyone still wants me to mail it the old fashion way, I'll be happy to.
But this may be a lot quicker, and you can check out our other stuff.

We have a list of book recommendations and they are linked to Amazon so you
can read reviews on them, and purchase them new or used if you wish.

There will be links to loads of cool unschooling, attachment parenting and
fun stuff to do sites. Book and magazine recommendations, essays on
unschooling and more.

Hope some of you come visit the L.I.F.E. support group site. (Learning in
Freedom Everyday)
It's at www.pensacolaunschoolers.com

Ren
